dct_description_sm: Map on verso: relevant sites are shown pictorially; tourist sites and museums are located. Includes Metro lines diagram, Metrobus route, and Caracas statistical data Includes phone directory with several useful numbers, including medical services, embassies, and taxi services. Includes an AT&T advertisement - "The easy way to call the States from Venezuela"
dct_publisher_sm: Isla de Margarita, Venezuela : Proyectum International C.A., 2000.
